        <div id="gameplay" class="tab-content">

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Core Rotation</h2>
                <p>The Death Trap Rogue follows a strict rotation. Once you hit the CDR and Energy thresholds, this loop sustains itself infinitely.</p>

                <ol class="rotation-steps">
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Dash through packs</strong> -- Engage with Dash to build Momentum stacks and position yourself in the center of enemy density.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Drop Caltrops</strong> -- Place your buff zone on the ground where enemies are grouped. This increases damage dealt to enemies standing in the area.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Concealment</strong> -- Activate Stealth for guaranteed 100% Critical Strike Chance, apply Vulnerable to all nearby enemies, and gain Unstoppable. Opportunist's Aspect launches grenades on stealth break.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Death Trap</strong> -- Drop the nuke. Enemies are pulled to center and obliterated. Eyes in the Dark immediately re-arms the trap for a second detonation, effectively doubling the hit.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Preparation auto-triggers</strong> -- The Energy spent from Death Trap and your rotation fills the Preparation meter. It resets Death Trap's cooldown and all other cooldowns automatically.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Evade/Dash + Grenade procs</strong> -- Reposition with Evade or Dash. Aspect of Artful Initiative and Opportunist's Aspect proc grenade bursts passively from your Energy spending and Stealth usage.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Repeat infinitely</strong> -- With enough CDR (10s Death Trap) and Energy (150+), this loop never breaks. Every Death Trap reset feeds the next cycle.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
