                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Always Conceal before Death Trap</strong>
                    <p>The 100% Crit + Vulnerable window from Concealment is your single largest damage amplifier. Skipping it cuts your damage by more than half.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Caltrops placement matters</strong>
                    <p>Drop Caltrops where enemies will be when Death Trap detonates, not where they currently are. Death Trap's pull effect moves enemies -- anticipate the final position.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Monitor your Energy bar</strong>
                    <p>If you drop below the Preparation threshold, the loop breaks. Use Ultimate Resource Restore temper and Ring of Starless Skies to maintain Energy flow. If the loop breaks, use basic attacks or wait for natural regen before re-entering.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Swap Key Passive for farming</strong>
                    <p>Use Exposure for Pit pushing (more damage amplification) and swap to Momentum for speed farming (stacking move-speed from Dash and Evade usage).</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
